            <p>Empowering education with a seamless student management system. Our goal is to enhance academic workflows and create an efficient environment for institutions.</p>
            <p><strong>Join us in revolutionizing education through technology!</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 quick-links">
            <h5 class="text-light">Quick Links</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled" style="font-weight: bold;">
              <li><a href="/pp" class="text-light">Home</a></li>
